	<description>
		<![CDATA[
		<div class="overview-header">
			<h2>
			  <small style="display: block;">Responsive Joomla template for decor and interior design - <strong>JA Decor</strong>.</small>
			</h2>
			<p>Responsive Joomla template for Decor, Interior Design and corporate portfolio for both Joomla 2.5 and Joomla 3 - <strong>JA Decor</strong>. A want-to-be-different Joomla template that will let not let you down, JA Decor is unique with its dynamic block layout design, eCommerce solution ready with Mijoshop component and is blogging friendly thanks to EasyBlog component. 
Built on the robust T3 Framework with Bootstrap 3 at core, <strong>JA Decor</strong> is fully responsive. WIth no exception, <strong>JA Decor</strong> supports Right-to-Left (RTL) language layoutand Off-Canvas menu navigation system for both mobile and tablet devices. 
</p>
			</div>
		]]>
	</description>
